# Notion PDF Exporter

## Description

This is a simple tool to export Notion pages to PDF.

## Installation

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Configuration

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

## Environment Variables

```bash
NOTION_API_KEY=your_notion_api_key
```

## Usage

```bash
python index.py
```
